= ActiveResourceIntegrationDSL (ARID) ChangeLog

== 0.4 -- ??/??/?? UNRELEASED
Bug Fixes
* Create RDoc-able documentation
		
Ehancements
* add option to add HTTP headers to requests
* add support for textarea and select fields
* add support for nested resource paths
		
== 0.3 -- 06/27/07
Bug Fixes
* fix so that tests can access the index action of controllers.

Misc.
* Updates to the readme
* smal typo fixes
	
== 0.2 -- 06/22/07
Bug Fixes
* end of session now logs user out with sessions/destroy

Enhancements
* add sess.exercises_<thing> method
* add support for AJAX requests
* add support to pass params to read and destroy actions.
	
Misc.
* Change name from RestfulCrudIntegrationTester to
	ActiveResourceIntegrationDsl (ARID)
* add blog URL to LICENSE file
* README file updated
	
